snippet.title: Wayward Harbor Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Wayward Harbour is a first-person horror game. Where you use a handheld mirror to escape from a terror revealing itself of the deeps of the ocean.

Download for free now on https://forild.itch.io/wayward-harbor

Team:
Environment/Level Design - Daniil Shashenkov
Props / Sound design - Lars Korden
Creature Design / Animation - Christopher Null
Gameplay Features / Mechanics - Tarnover Vitaly
AI / Game loop - Martijn Dhondt 
Composer - Gonçalo Oliveira
